data.description: The large single story Santa Maria II floor plan by Lennar features an inviting front porch and entry foyer that leads to the family room. The kitchen features an adjoining breakfast room with access to the backyard. The master bedroom features an en suite master bathroom with a shower and the option to add dual sinks, and a large master closet. The Santa Maria II floor plan also features a full secondary bathroom and three secondary bedrooms.
